  <name>Venus Pro Config</name>
  <summary>Configuration utility for UtechSmart Venus Pro MMO Mouse</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Venus Pro Config is a powerful Linux utility for configuring the UtechSmart Venus Pro MMO Gaming Mouse.
      It works with both the Wireless (Pro) and Wired versions of the mouse.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Full button remapping for all 16 buttons</li>
      <li>Macro recording and management</li>
      <li>RGB lighting configuration (Neon, Breathing, Steady)</li>
      <li>DPI profile settings (up to 16000 DPI)</li>
      <li>Polling rate adjustment (125Hz - 1000Hz)</li>
      <li>Profile management (save/load configurations)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
